Class CarModelSpecification

  • java.lang.Object
    • businessmodel.CarModelSpecification

  • public class CarModelSpecification
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a car model specification. It gives an overview of lists of Components that are available for a car model.
    Author:
    SWOP Team 10
